name: Naruto
synopsis: Naruto Uzumaki, a young ninja, seeks recognition and dreams of becoming Hokage while facing powerful enemies and uncovering secrets of his past.

name: Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood
synopsis: Two brothers, Edward and Alphonse Elric, use alchemy to try to resurrect their mother, suffering grave consequences, and then seek the Philosopher's Stone to restore their bodies.

name: Attack on Titan
synopsis: Humanity fights for survival against giant humanoid Titans that devour humans, while uncovering dark secrets about their world.

name: Death Note
synopsis: A high school student gains a notebook that allows him to kill anyone whose name he writes in it, leading to a high-stakes battle of wits with a genius detective.

name: My Hero Academia
synopsis: In a world where nearly everyone has superpowers called Quirks, Izuku Midoriya dreams of becoming a hero despite being born Quirkless.

name: One Piece
synopsis: Monkey D. Luffy and his crew of pirates explore the Grand Line to find the ultimate treasure, the One Piece, and become the Pirate King.

name: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba
synopsis: Tanjiro Kamado becomes a demon slayer after his family is slaughtered by demons, seeking a cure for his sister Nezuko who was turned into a demon.

name: Tokyo Revengers
synopsis: Takemichi Hanagaki travels back in time to his middle school days to save his ex-girlfriend from a tragic fate and change the future of a gang.

name: Jujutsu Kaisen
synopsis: Yuji Itadori joins a secret organization to fight Curses after swallowing a powerful cursed object, facing dangerous opponents and uncovering dark mysteries.

name: Hunter x Hunter
synopsis: Gon Freecss becomes a Hunter to find his missing father, encountering dangerous challenges, friends, and deadly foes along the way.

name: Vinland Saga
synopsis: Thorfinn seeks revenge against the mercenary leader who killed his father while being drawn into the violent world of Vikings, war, and honor.
